1
00:00:01,040 --> 00:00:03,710
(Episode 86)

2
00:00:07,580 --> 00:00:08,580
Move.

3
00:00:11,620 --> 00:00:14,290
(Suk Hee's Side Dishes)

4
00:00:16,590 --> 00:00:18,190
- Let's go in.
- Darn it!

5
00:00:18,590 --> 00:00:20,090
- Get in here!
- What's going on?

6
00:00:21,690 --> 00:00:22,930
What are you doing?

7
00:00:23,190 --> 00:00:24,230
Who are these guys?

8
00:00:24,500 --> 00:00:26,330
Hey! What do you think you're doing?

9
00:00:26,430 --> 00:00:30,200
My brother's on his deathbed
because he ate your side dishes!

10
00:00:30,370 --> 00:00:32,500
And you still have the nerve
to be open for business?

11
00:00:32,570 --> 00:00:34,570
Please, don't do this. Stop it!

12
00:00:35,270 --> 00:00:37,310
Tae Sook, stay back.
You're going to get hurt.

13
00:00:37,980 --> 00:00:39,940
Are you gangsters or something?

14
00:00:40,210 --> 00:00:41,610
Use your words!

15
00:00:41,680 --> 00:00:43,720
Who got sick from our food?

16
00:00:43,850 --> 00:00:46,050
This is your last day in business,
you hear me?

17
00:00:47,090 --> 00:00:49,420
- Stop it!
- I said, cut it out!

18
00:00:49,520 --> 00:00:50,520
Get out of the way!

19
00:00:51,160 --> 00:00:52,190
Tae Sook.

20
00:00:56,360 --> 00:00:59,330
They're scary. They're bad.
They're bad people.

21
00:00:59,500 --> 00:01:00,830
Call the police!

22
00:01:02,670 --> 00:01:04,340
Call the police!

23
00:01:04,870 --> 00:01:07,040
Hey! I said, cut it out!

24
00:01:07,570 --> 00:01:09,170
Smash that side too!

25
00:01:09,970 --> 00:01:12,080
What are you doing in my building?

26
00:01:12,080 --> 00:01:13,610
Who are you all?

27
00:01:14,280 --> 00:01:15,280
Hey!

28
00:01:15,280 --> 00:01:16,650
Get back here, you bastards!

29
00:01:30,090 --> 00:01:31,160
Welcome, my dear daughter.

30
00:01:33,060 --> 00:01:35,830
So you're finally getting married
to Kang Jun Ho.

31
00:01:36,400 --> 00:01:37,400
Oh Jang Mi.

32
00:01:38,070 --> 00:01:39,640
Who says I'm getting married?

33
00:01:40,140 --> 00:01:42,610
Chae Hwa Young,
do you really think you'll get your way?

34
00:01:46,980 --> 00:01:50,010
Do you really think you can avoid
marrying General Manager Kang?

35
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:52,980
In the end, you won't be able to resist,
and you will go through with it.

36
00:01:53,420 --> 00:01:56,290
- I guarantee it.
- Is he supposed to marry himself?

37
00:01:56,550 --> 00:01:59,460
I told you, didn't I?
I'm not marrying Kang Jun Ho.

38
00:01:59,860 --> 00:02:03,330
Do I need to spell it out for you?
The man I love is Kang Baek Ho.

39
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:06,630
I will never marry General Manager Kang.

40
00:02:06,730 --> 00:02:09,600
You're destined to marry
Kang Jun Ho anyway.

41
00:02:10,030 --> 00:02:12,840
And you know why?
Because I'll make sure of it.

42
00:02:13,670 --> 00:02:15,470
Chae Hwa Young, dream on!

43
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:18,080
Because I'll never let you
get what you want.

44
00:02:18,310 --> 00:02:21,210
While Grandfather has his eyes wide open,

45
00:02:21,550 --> 00:02:23,110
do you really think you'll get your way?

46
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:26,620
Oh Jang Mi. You've gotten quite vicious.

47
00:02:27,590 --> 00:02:28,650
Don't get cocky.

48
00:02:29,020 --> 00:02:31,320
- Do you really think you're Seo Rin?
- Shut up!

49
00:02:31,590 --> 00:02:32,960
If you mess with Seo Rin,

50
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:35,060
I swear I'll drag you
to the abyss with me.

51
00:02:36,530 --> 00:02:38,530
Do you really think you're Ma Seo Rin?

52
00:02:38,660 --> 00:02:40,600
Do you think you could ever become her?

53
00:02:40,770 --> 00:02:43,740
Don't kid yourself. You're just a fake,
an imitation of Seo Rin.

54
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:45,240
You can never be the real thing.

55
00:02:45,670 --> 00:02:47,240
- What?
- Get this straight.

56
00:02:47,810 --> 00:02:50,940
You're nothing but a puppet
who has to do whatever I say. Got it?

57
00:02:51,110 --> 00:02:52,640
Know your place.

58
00:02:55,750 --> 00:02:57,720
I think you're the one who needs
to know her place.

59
00:02:58,080 --> 00:03:01,150
If Grandfather finds out the secrets
you're so desperate to hide,

60
00:03:01,220 --> 00:03:02,450
what do you think will happen to you?

61
00:03:03,050 --> 00:03:05,060
- What?
- The moment I tell Grandfather...

62
00:03:05,060 --> 00:03:07,330
everything you're desperately
trying to hide,

63
00:03:07,630 --> 00:03:09,490
it's over for you. Don't you get it?

64
00:03:10,030 --> 00:03:13,460
Oh Jang Mi.
You’ve got quite the mouth on you.

65
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:16,200
It sounds like
you want to see your grandfather die.

66
00:03:16,600 --> 00:03:18,500
If so, go on and tell him.
I won't stop you.

67
00:03:19,500 --> 00:03:20,840
What are you so confident about?

68
00:03:20,940 --> 00:03:24,010
Oh Jang Mi.
You think your family will be safe then?

69
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:29,680
Answer it...

70
00:03:30,010 --> 00:03:31,880
if you care about your family's safety.

71
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:34,590
Chae Hwa Young, what have you done now?

72
00:03:37,190 --> 00:03:39,520
Tae Pyung, is Mom okay?

73
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:40,690
She's safe, right?

74
00:03:41,130 --> 00:03:42,130
Don't even ask.

75
00:03:42,330 --> 00:03:44,630
Gangsters came
and completely trashed the place and left.

76
00:03:45,030 --> 00:03:48,170
It's okay, Bo Ra.
You don't have to be scared anymore.

77
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:50,740
Gangsters? What are you talking about?

78
00:03:50,740 --> 00:03:52,840
Oh Jang Mi, this is just a taste.

79
00:03:53,440 --> 00:03:55,540
The more you refuse to play along,

80
00:03:55,810 --> 00:03:58,280
the more those around you will suffer.
You need to understand that.

81
00:03:58,610 --> 00:04:00,450
Especially your family. Got it?

82
00:04:01,250 --> 00:04:04,450
Tae Pyung, I'll call you back.
I have to go now.

83
00:04:06,020 --> 00:04:08,550
I told you, didn't I?
This is only the beginning.

84
00:04:10,090 --> 00:04:11,590
You shameless monster!

85
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:12,960
How dare you!

86
00:04:14,290 --> 00:04:16,090
You should have left my family
out of this.

87
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:19,800
Why drag my innocent family into this?
Why?

88
00:04:19,860 --> 00:04:21,000
Then do as I say!

89
00:04:21,870 --> 00:04:24,300
Marry Kang Jun Ho. It's that simple.

90
00:04:24,370 --> 00:04:27,440
In your dreams.
I will never let you have your way.

91
00:04:28,470 --> 00:04:30,740
What? Are you in love with Kang Baek Ho?

92
00:04:32,610 --> 00:04:35,710
If you want to protect Kang Baek Ho,
you'd be wise to do as I say.

93
00:04:37,080 --> 00:04:38,980
- Chae Hwa Young!
- Oh, my.

94
00:04:39,750 --> 00:04:41,020
It's time to go...

95
00:04:41,090 --> 00:04:42,720
to General Manager Kang's home
for the wedding preparations.

96
00:04:43,320 --> 00:04:44,590
I was invited.

97
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:49,190
What on earth happened here?

98
00:04:49,760 --> 00:04:52,030
You think you can wreck this store?

99
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:53,160
We're so sorry.

100
00:04:53,630 --> 00:04:55,230
We'll pay for all the damages.

101
00:04:55,730 --> 00:04:58,200
- You must have been shocked, sir.
- Shocked is an understatement!

102
00:04:58,570 --> 00:05:02,310
Seriously, why is this family
plagued by so much trouble?

103
00:05:02,470 --> 00:05:05,280
- What is going on here?
- Tell me about it.

104
00:05:05,380 --> 00:05:07,010
We're devastated, too.

105
00:05:07,350 --> 00:05:10,880
Why does all the bad luck
pile up on our family?

106
00:05:12,380 --> 00:05:14,320
- Oh, for crying out loud.
- Tae Sook...

107
00:05:14,390 --> 00:05:16,020
What a mess.

108
00:05:16,650 --> 00:05:17,660
Goodness.

109
00:05:23,960 --> 00:05:28,070
You shouldn't have.
You always bring so much.

110
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:31,070
I'll wait in the car, then.

111
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:34,240
Thank you, Manager Lee.

112
00:05:37,010 --> 00:05:38,010
It must be...

113
00:05:38,440 --> 00:05:41,280
reassuring to have someone
like Manager Lee by your side.

114
00:05:41,610 --> 00:05:42,610
It is.

115
00:05:43,180 --> 00:05:45,520
By the way,
with what happened to Jun Ho...

116
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:48,720
and that news story about me,
you must have been quite shocked.

117
00:05:49,990 --> 00:05:53,260
We were a little. It was all so absurd.

118
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:55,860
You were surprised too,
weren't you, honey?

119
00:05:56,560 --> 00:05:58,200
Yes, I was.

120
00:05:58,800 --> 00:06:00,500
I was the one who caused the accident,

121
00:06:00,830 --> 00:06:02,830
but CEO Chae was the one who went to jail.

122
00:06:02,830 --> 00:06:04,140
How could I not be surprised?

123
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:08,810
It's unbelievable, isn't it?

124
00:06:08,810 --> 00:06:09,870
Tell me about it.

125
00:06:10,610 --> 00:06:12,840
They say you see
all sorts of things in life,

126
00:06:13,310 --> 00:06:14,880
but this incident was so preposterous...

127
00:06:15,280 --> 00:06:17,050
that I'm almost too embarrassed
to speak of it.

128
00:06:17,550 --> 00:06:21,520
But I heard it was Oh Jang Mi
who reported you?

129
00:06:21,750 --> 00:06:24,090
It just goes to show that
no good deed goes unpunished.

130
00:06:24,820 --> 00:06:27,160
I even found a job for her brother,

131
00:06:27,660 --> 00:06:30,600
and I was even going to pay for Oh Jang Mi
to study abroad.

132
00:06:31,100 --> 00:06:32,130
I guess it's true what they say.

133
00:06:32,130 --> 00:06:33,800
"Give someone an inch,
and they'll take a mile."

134
00:06:34,030 --> 00:06:36,530
Who knew she would turn on me
with such a vengeance?

135
00:06:37,270 --> 00:06:39,340
By the way,
I hear General Manager Kang Jun Ho...

136
00:06:39,340 --> 00:06:40,570
is getting out of the hospital?

137
00:06:40,770 --> 00:06:43,310
Yes, he's doing much better now.

138
00:06:43,610 --> 00:06:46,280
And Jun Ho is getting restless
in the hospital.

139
00:06:47,980 --> 00:06:50,520
I feel so terrible about everything
that's happened.

140
00:06:50,780 --> 00:06:52,520
It's not your fault.

141
00:06:53,020 --> 00:06:57,290
And we're just so thankful
it wasn't worse for our Jun Ho.

142
00:06:59,760 --> 00:07:00,960
I believe the Chairman...

143
00:07:01,590 --> 00:07:04,500
was moved
by General Manager Kang's love...

144
00:07:04,500 --> 00:07:05,930
for my daughter.

145
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:11,640
That's why he's so insistent
that Seo Rin and Jun Ho get married.

146
00:07:12,140 --> 00:07:13,140
Pardon?

147
00:07:14,770 --> 00:07:18,380
So the Chairman has taken a liking
to our Jun Ho?

148
00:07:19,180 --> 00:07:22,780
Absolutely.
The reason I stopped by today...

149
00:07:23,010 --> 00:07:25,520
is that the Chairman urged me
to hurry the wedding along.

150
00:07:26,450 --> 00:07:29,690
That's why I've come,
even though Jun Ho is still recovering.

151
00:07:31,690 --> 00:07:32,960
In that case,

152
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:36,130
we should set a wedding date
for them right away.

153
00:07:39,430 --> 00:07:41,300
Oh my, you must be hungry.

154
00:07:41,830 --> 00:07:42,900
Just a moment.

155
00:08:06,320 --> 00:08:09,530
Hwa Young.
So this is really the end for us.

156
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:20,100
Hwa Young, what are you doing in here?

157
00:08:24,810 --> 00:08:26,080
It's over between us, isn't it?

158
00:08:28,450 --> 00:08:30,650
You've been thinking that, too?

159
00:08:32,380 --> 00:08:34,250
The thought of breaking up with you,
Nam Bong,

160
00:08:34,850 --> 00:08:36,520
makes my heart feel like it is breaking.

161
00:08:37,460 --> 00:08:38,460
Hwa Young...

162
00:08:39,860 --> 00:08:43,330
With the Chairman acting like this,
my hands are tied now.

163
00:08:45,160 --> 00:08:46,260
What are we going to do?

164
00:08:47,670 --> 00:08:49,700
No... My wife is right outside.

165
00:08:50,600 --> 00:08:52,970
Let's talk later, okay?

166
00:09:09,890 --> 00:09:14,530
Honey, are you really planning on marrying
Seo Rin to General Manager Kang?

167
00:09:14,790 --> 00:09:15,790
Yes.

168
00:09:16,690 --> 00:09:20,800
Mrs. Yeom, you handle the preparations
for our Seo Rin's wedding.

169
00:09:20,930 --> 00:09:24,270
If we're marrying her off,
we'll have to set them up with a new home.

170
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:27,170
Where are you thinking of setting them up?

171
00:09:27,670 --> 00:09:31,440
Why would I send my precious girl away?
It's not like I have much longer to live.

172
00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:34,480
I'm just going to keep her here with me
until the day I die.

173
00:09:35,150 --> 00:09:36,280
And you'd better understand that,
Mrs. Yeom.

174
00:09:37,010 --> 00:09:39,120
Yes. Of course.

175
00:09:42,890 --> 00:09:43,960
But, honey...

176
00:09:45,590 --> 00:09:46,620
Can I get a credit card...

177
00:09:47,830 --> 00:09:50,590
This is a wedding for the granddaughter
of the great Dream Group.

178
00:09:50,660 --> 00:09:53,500
We have to go all out, don't we?

179
00:09:58,400 --> 00:10:02,170
I seem to recall giving you one before.

180
00:10:03,270 --> 00:10:04,810
Make sure you only use this...

181
00:10:05,340 --> 00:10:07,110
for Seo Rin's marriage.

182
00:10:08,510 --> 00:10:11,280
Of course. Absolutely.
You can count on it.

183
00:10:12,880 --> 00:10:15,450
What? You want to go buy designer clothes?

184
00:10:17,020 --> 00:10:18,620
Where do you have the money for that?

185
00:10:18,960 --> 00:10:21,490
You don't have a penny to your name
since you lost all your shares in crypto.

186
00:10:21,590 --> 00:10:24,660
You little brat.
Crypto was just a bad investment.

187
00:10:24,800 --> 00:10:28,800
I was trying to make money,
not trying to throw it all away, you know.

188
00:10:30,940 --> 00:10:34,140
Anyway, I got the Chairman's black card.

189
00:10:34,770 --> 00:10:36,440
- Really?
- Yes.

190
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:39,840
After all I've put up with in this home,
what joy do I have to live for?

191
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:41,350
I deserve to have some fun spending money.

192
00:10:42,280 --> 00:10:45,620
Mom, I need to get all dressed up, then.

193
00:10:45,620 --> 00:10:48,020
I always look
like some freeloader servant.

194
00:10:48,850 --> 00:10:50,550
I've been walking on eggshells
around Chae Hwa Young,

195
00:10:50,550 --> 00:10:52,260
and I couldn't even spend a dime freely.

196
00:10:52,490 --> 00:10:54,290
By the way, Hong Ju.

197
00:10:54,960 --> 00:10:58,230
About Oh Jang Mi being
at that rehab hospital,

198
00:10:58,600 --> 00:11:00,430
should we tell Chae Hwa Young about it?

199
00:11:00,600 --> 00:11:03,900
We haven't even seen with our own eyes
that Oh Jang Mi is there.

200
00:11:04,170 --> 00:11:07,170
- Because that burly nurse blocked us.
- Right?

201
00:11:08,510 --> 00:11:11,080
But still, what's with Chae Hwa Young?

202
00:11:11,440 --> 00:11:14,750
Why isn't she pushing us to find her?

203
00:11:14,810 --> 00:11:15,950
I know, right?

204
00:11:16,380 --> 00:11:18,520
You think she found her?

205
00:11:18,520 --> 00:11:20,820
What? It'd be stranger if she did.

206
00:11:21,190 --> 00:11:24,520
She's her daughter.
It's weird she'd find her and say nothing.

207
00:11:26,160 --> 00:11:27,160
Who knows?

208
00:11:27,690 --> 00:11:30,360
(Bomdama)

209
00:11:30,490 --> 00:11:31,500
Wait, what did you just say?

210
00:11:31,900 --> 00:11:33,400
CEO Chae went after
the side dish shop too?

211
00:11:33,760 --> 00:11:36,470
Yes. I'm so incredibly upset.

212
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:38,540
That's unbelievable. Seriously.

213
00:11:39,170 --> 00:11:42,310
I can't believe she'd threaten your family
just to marry you off to my brother.

214
00:11:42,370 --> 00:11:43,510
And that's not all.

215
00:11:43,910 --> 00:11:45,780
You must be really careful too, Baek Ho.

216
00:11:45,910 --> 00:11:47,680
She said she's coming after you as well.

217
00:11:47,750 --> 00:11:49,210
Darn it, that woman!

218
00:11:49,310 --> 00:11:52,420
For my sake,
please don't get hurt, Baek Ho.

219
00:11:52,550 --> 00:11:54,420
- Promise?
- Don't worry.

220
00:11:55,090 --> 00:11:56,850
I'm more worried about you.

221
00:11:57,190 --> 00:11:59,620
Considering how hard she's trying to
marry me off to General Manager Kang,

222
00:11:59,690 --> 00:12:01,760
I don't think she'll touch me
for the time being.

223
00:12:02,230 --> 00:12:05,260
Right now, Chae Hwa Young's goal is
my marriage to General Manager Kang.

224
00:12:05,460 --> 00:12:07,000
That's a relief, but still...

225
00:12:07,730 --> 00:12:11,300
I just don't get why my brother is
suddenly so set on marrying you.

226
00:12:11,370 --> 00:12:15,110
Baek Ho, I have an ace up my sleeve
to stop him,

227
00:12:15,170 --> 00:12:16,170
so don't you worry.

228
00:12:16,670 --> 00:12:17,680
And what's that?

229
00:12:19,180 --> 00:12:22,650
Let's eat first. We'll talk after.

230
00:12:31,720 --> 00:12:34,230
(Suk Hee's Side Dishes)

231
00:12:39,460 --> 00:12:41,300
Tae Pyung, you're going to hurt your hand.

232
00:12:42,730 --> 00:12:45,440
I have no idea
how far Chae Hwa Young will go.

233
00:12:46,370 --> 00:12:47,370
Tell me about it.

234
00:12:47,810 --> 00:12:51,240
As if hiding Seo Rin wasn't enough,
now she's using her marriage as a threat.

235
00:12:53,710 --> 00:12:54,710
Baek Ho.

236
00:12:55,580 --> 00:12:56,650
What are we going to do...

237
00:12:57,110 --> 00:12:59,050
if Jang Mi really does marry your brother?

238
00:13:00,890 --> 00:13:02,220
I can't even stand the thought of it.

239
00:13:02,420 --> 00:13:04,020
Come on, that's not going to happen.
Don't worry.

240
00:13:04,460 --> 00:13:06,290
I'll do whatever it takes
to stop that wedding.

241
00:13:14,600 --> 00:13:15,900
Please, have some, Seo Rin.

242
00:13:16,530 --> 00:13:20,270
It's okay. I'll eat with my grandfather
when I get home.

243
00:13:27,950 --> 00:13:29,710
This is absolutely delicious, you know.

244
00:13:30,180 --> 00:13:33,350
It's the least I can do
after you saved me.

245
00:13:33,620 --> 00:13:35,290
But if this is all the "service" I get,

246
00:13:35,350 --> 00:13:37,820
it's a pretty weak reward
for saving your life.

247
00:13:38,260 --> 00:13:41,530
If you keep being so pushy,
you won't get anything at all.

248
00:13:42,890 --> 00:13:45,000
- All done?
- Yes.

249
00:13:57,710 --> 00:13:58,880
This is CEO Chae's spoon.

250
00:14:03,710 --> 00:14:04,950
Thank you, Geum Soon.

251
00:14:05,650 --> 00:14:07,450
Are you going for the DNA test right away?

252
00:14:07,820 --> 00:14:09,220
Yes, I have to.

253
00:14:10,290 --> 00:14:13,190
Once I can prove that Chae Hwa Young is
Kang Jun Ho's mother,

254
00:14:13,520 --> 00:14:15,360
I'm going to show the proof
to Grandfather.

255
00:14:16,030 --> 00:14:20,730
That way, he'll know what she's planning
by forcing me to marry Kang Jun Ho.

256
00:14:20,930 --> 00:14:23,300
Then the Chairman will
surely understand...

257
00:14:23,900 --> 00:14:26,770
just how much of a threat CEO Chae is
to the company.

258
00:14:27,170 --> 00:14:29,440
But that alone will be a huge shock
to Grandfather.

259
00:14:30,010 --> 00:14:31,610
I don't know if he'll be okay.

260
00:14:40,020 --> 00:14:42,690
What are you carrying out of the kitchen?

261
00:14:44,150 --> 00:14:45,390
Mom, you're just getting home?

262
00:14:45,460 --> 00:14:47,360
I asked you what you're carrying.

263
00:14:49,460 --> 00:14:51,200
Why are you making such a big deal?

264
00:14:51,330 --> 00:14:52,400
You're being suspicious.

265
00:14:53,000 --> 00:14:54,100
Give me that bag.

266
00:14:56,530 --> 00:14:57,530
Now.

267
00:14:59,040 --> 00:15:01,810
You've got to be kidding me.
Why are you demanding to see my bag?

268
00:15:01,910 --> 00:15:03,870
What is this, school?
Are you going to start doing bag checks?

269
00:15:03,940 --> 00:15:05,710
What could you possibly have to hide
from your mother?

270
00:15:06,010 --> 00:15:07,010
Give it to me now.

271
00:15:09,210 --> 00:15:10,380
What's going on here?

272
00:15:12,920 --> 00:15:13,920
Grandfather.

273
00:15:14,180 --> 00:15:17,120
Look at Mom.
She's trying to go through my bag.

274
00:15:17,960 --> 00:15:20,560
After everything I've said.

275
00:15:20,620 --> 00:15:23,760
Last time, you went nuts over her phone,

276
00:15:23,760 --> 00:15:25,830
and now you want to search her bag?

277
00:15:26,060 --> 00:15:29,330
Even if she is your daughter,
she's entitled to her privacy.

278
00:15:31,470 --> 00:15:32,470
Yes, Father.

279
00:15:36,510 --> 00:15:37,840
Thanks, Grandfather!

280
00:15:39,680 --> 00:15:40,680
You're something else.

281
00:15:56,630 --> 00:15:57,630
Manager Lee.

282
00:15:57,960 --> 00:16:01,430
Oh Jang Mi just left the house.
See where she goes with that bag.

283
00:16:07,970 --> 00:16:09,340
Jang Mi, what are you doing here?

284
00:16:09,340 --> 00:16:11,240
It's not safe to be here.
Why did you come here?

285
00:16:11,410 --> 00:16:13,180
How could I just sit around
and do nothing?

286
00:16:14,110 --> 00:16:16,650
Tae Pyung, you and Mom must have been
so scared, right?

287
00:16:17,150 --> 00:16:19,720
- Is Mom okay?
- She and Bo Ra couldn't stop crying.

288
00:16:21,050 --> 00:16:22,920
Chae Hwa Young, that monster.

289
00:16:23,420 --> 00:16:25,260
How dare she come after our family?

290
00:16:28,730 --> 00:16:32,300
Chae Hwa Young.
You must have had your people tailing me.

291
00:16:32,900 --> 00:16:35,170
Did you really think
I'd go straight to the DNA lab?

292
00:16:36,030 --> 00:16:37,030
Not a chance.

293
00:16:38,170 --> 00:16:39,270
Yes, Manager Lee?

294
00:16:39,670 --> 00:16:41,740
My guys say
she went into a side dish shop.

295
00:16:42,110 --> 00:16:43,110
Is that so?

296
00:16:44,170 --> 00:16:45,180
Oh Jang Mi.

297
00:16:45,540 --> 00:16:49,080
So she's just feeding her siblings
some scraps of meat?

298
00:16:50,010 --> 00:16:53,950
She's so poor, what she snuck out
is probably just worthless veggie scraps.

299
00:16:54,690 --> 00:16:55,820
All right, call them off.

300
00:17:04,060 --> 00:17:06,960
Jun Ho.
Go lie down in your room for a while.

301
00:17:07,300 --> 00:17:10,030
I'll heat up some bone broth.
Come out and eat once the table is set.

302
00:17:10,230 --> 00:17:11,670
Mom, I'm all right now.

303
00:17:12,200 --> 00:17:13,400
I'll have the broth now, please.

304
00:17:14,340 --> 00:17:16,510
- You sure?
- Are you really okay?

305
00:17:17,070 --> 00:17:19,780
You still need to be careful
so the wound doesn't get infected.

306
00:17:20,780 --> 00:17:22,510
Yes, don't worry.

307
00:17:22,850 --> 00:17:23,950
By the way, Jun Ho.

308
00:17:24,420 --> 00:17:28,120
I heard Chairman Ma gave his blessing
for you and Seo Rin to marry.

309
00:17:30,150 --> 00:17:32,220
- Really?
- Yes.

310
00:17:33,990 --> 00:17:36,360
After I eat,
I'll head into the office for a bit.

311
00:17:36,630 --> 00:17:37,860
What? Already?

312
00:17:38,200 --> 00:17:39,960
Now that the Chairman
gave us his blessing,

313
00:17:40,360 --> 00:17:41,430
I feel completely re-energized.

314
00:17:42,070 --> 00:17:43,370
And I'm curious about the office, too.

315
00:17:43,700 --> 00:17:45,340
You're not curious about work.

316
00:17:45,970 --> 00:17:48,210
You just want to see Ma Seo Rin,
don't you?

317
00:17:50,510 --> 00:17:54,210
All right. Go on,
and you two should discuss a wedding date.

318
00:18:02,720 --> 00:18:05,520
Are you sure you should be back
at work so soon?

319
00:18:07,160 --> 00:18:08,490
I missed you so much, Seo Rin,

320
00:18:09,090 --> 00:18:11,860
- that I just couldn't stay home.
- Excuse me?

321
00:18:13,360 --> 00:18:14,830
You've become quite the jokester.

322
00:18:15,600 --> 00:18:19,700
Anyway,
I hope your arm heals completely soon.

323
00:18:21,470 --> 00:18:22,470
Wait a second.

324
00:18:26,910 --> 00:18:28,210
Seo Rin, you heard, didn't you?

325
00:18:29,080 --> 00:18:30,880
That the Chairman approved our marriage.

326
00:18:32,950 --> 00:18:34,380
I told him I didn't want to.

327
00:18:35,120 --> 00:18:37,420
I'm not going to marry you, Jun Ho.

328
00:18:37,650 --> 00:18:39,860
But I am going to marry you, Seo Rin.

329
00:18:40,220 --> 00:18:42,430
What, are you going to marry yourself?

330
00:18:42,860 --> 00:18:44,800
Why are you doing this?
I already said I won't marry you.

331
00:18:47,430 --> 00:18:48,700
I love you, Seo Rin.

332
00:18:51,200 --> 00:18:52,200
Well...

333
00:18:52,900 --> 00:18:55,610
I'm in love with your brother,
Kang Baek Ho.

334
00:18:56,140 --> 00:18:57,770
There. Is that clear enough for you?

335
00:18:58,140 --> 00:18:59,880
Why my brother, of all people?

336
00:19:01,410 --> 00:19:02,550
Since when?

337
00:19:03,710 --> 00:19:05,620
But you were the one
who wanted to marry me.

338
00:19:06,150 --> 00:19:08,190
Why did you change your mind
after the accident?

339
00:19:08,890 --> 00:19:12,090
I'll apologize for everything
I've done to disappoint you.

340
00:19:13,060 --> 00:19:16,430
This isn't something an apology can fix.

341
00:19:20,060 --> 00:19:23,000
You asked me
when I fell in love with Baek Ho.

342
00:19:23,570 --> 00:19:24,600
Well...

343
00:19:25,300 --> 00:19:26,800
Even before I met you,

344
00:19:27,540 --> 00:19:29,610
I was in love with Baek Ho
from the very start.

345
00:19:30,240 --> 00:19:31,310
Does that answer your question?

346
00:19:31,580 --> 00:19:32,580
What?

347
00:19:33,980 --> 00:19:35,110
What does that even mean?

348
00:19:36,450 --> 00:19:37,510
If you...

349
00:19:38,120 --> 00:19:39,820
keep insisting that
you're going to marry me,

350
00:19:40,320 --> 00:19:41,390
then I'll have no other choice...

351
00:19:42,250 --> 00:19:43,720
but to tell you the entire truth.

352
00:19:44,560 --> 00:19:45,920
The truth? What are you talking about?

353
00:19:47,190 --> 00:19:48,190
I'm...

354
00:19:48,860 --> 00:19:50,190
not Ma Seo Rin.

355
00:19:51,160 --> 00:19:52,260
I'm Oh Jang Mi.

356
00:19:53,130 --> 00:19:54,160
What did you just say?

357
00:19:54,160 --> 00:19:55,730
I'm Oh Jang Mi.

358
00:19:58,800 --> 00:20:00,540
- What?
- Seo Rin and I...

359
00:20:01,570 --> 00:20:02,670
are twins.

360
00:20:08,580 --> 00:20:09,580
What did you just say?

361
00:20:11,250 --> 00:20:13,920
What? You're telling me
Jun Ho came in to work...

362
00:20:14,220 --> 00:20:15,490
the moment he got out of the hospital?

363
00:20:15,750 --> 00:20:17,720
Yes, he's in his office right now.

364
00:20:18,760 --> 00:20:22,260
Why is he pushing himself like this?
He should be resting.

365
00:20:22,490 --> 00:20:24,230
Don't you think he came
because he missed Oh Jang Mi?

366
00:20:25,230 --> 00:20:27,230
And now that Chairman Ma has approved
their marriage,

367
00:20:28,000 --> 00:20:29,170
he probably wants to talk to her about it.

368
00:20:30,400 --> 00:20:33,270
Is he that infatuated with Oh Jang Mi?
Kang Jun Ho.

369
00:20:33,640 --> 00:20:37,040
You're my son.
You should be driven by ambition alone.

370
00:20:37,770 --> 00:20:39,540
Why are you losing your head
over some worthless girl?

371
00:20:39,780 --> 00:20:41,610
There's no stopping love.

372
00:20:43,150 --> 00:20:44,410
This is so frustrating
that I could scream.

373
00:20:46,120 --> 00:20:47,150
Oh Jang Mi.

374
00:20:47,780 --> 00:20:51,620
Just how did you manage to seduce my son?
That sly little vixen.

375
00:20:53,720 --> 00:20:55,490
So you're saying that of the two twins,

376
00:20:55,990 --> 00:20:57,830
Chae Hwa Young stole
Seo Rin and raised her?

377
00:20:57,960 --> 00:20:59,100
And that's not all.

378
00:21:00,060 --> 00:21:03,670
You remember when CEO Chae was detained
not too long ago, right?

379
00:21:04,740 --> 00:21:05,740
That was because...

380
00:21:06,500 --> 00:21:08,310
CEO Chae had my father killed
after he found out...

381
00:21:08,910 --> 00:21:10,570
the secret about the twins.

382
00:21:11,310 --> 00:21:14,040
And she even killed Ssangkal,
the man who turned himself in...

383
00:21:15,110 --> 00:21:16,110
to cover for her.

384
00:21:17,450 --> 00:21:19,220
- That's enough.
- It's hard, but you must hear this.

385
00:21:19,920 --> 00:21:21,320
You need to know the truth, Jun Ho.

386
00:21:22,850 --> 00:21:23,920
She's your mother, after all.

387
00:21:26,720 --> 00:21:29,860
You knew that CEO Chae is my birth mother?

388
00:21:31,460 --> 00:21:32,460
Yes.

389
00:21:33,660 --> 00:21:36,930
And CEO Chae knows that I'm Oh Jang Mi.

390
00:21:37,930 --> 00:21:39,670
Since you're her son,

391
00:21:40,040 --> 00:21:43,040
she insists you marry me,
the Chairman's true heir.

392
00:21:46,810 --> 00:21:49,710
I can't make sense of any of this.

393
00:21:50,780 --> 00:21:52,220
No, I can't believe any of it.

394
00:21:52,520 --> 00:21:53,580
I understand.

395
00:21:54,320 --> 00:21:55,350
You must be so confused.

396
00:21:56,050 --> 00:21:57,050
Then...

397
00:21:58,060 --> 00:21:59,760
where is the real Director Ma?

398
00:21:59,760 --> 00:22:00,860
That's exactly it.

399
00:22:01,320 --> 00:22:02,790
Seo Rin is in danger right now.

400
00:22:04,230 --> 00:22:05,300
CEO Chae...

401
00:22:05,860 --> 00:22:07,860
arranged a car accident to kill me,

402
00:22:08,830 --> 00:22:11,070
but Seo Rin and I were in it together.

403
00:22:11,870 --> 00:22:13,070
I only had minor injuries,

404
00:22:13,870 --> 00:22:16,140
but Seo Rin fell into a coma
and hasn't woken up since.

405
00:22:16,770 --> 00:22:18,510
But then, while Seo Rin was in a coma,

406
00:22:18,980 --> 00:22:20,910
CEO Chae took her away
and hid her somewhere.

407
00:22:21,380 --> 00:22:22,710
This is unbelievable.

408
00:22:22,980 --> 00:22:25,450
She only ever needed one of us...

409
00:22:25,780 --> 00:22:27,550
from the beginning...

410
00:22:28,290 --> 00:22:29,520
to deceive Grandfather...

411
00:22:29,520 --> 00:22:31,990
No, to take over Dream.

412
00:22:33,620 --> 00:22:38,130
And that's why Seo Rin
may die at CEO Chae's hands.

413
00:22:39,360 --> 00:22:41,260
Please save Seo Rin, Jun Ho.

414
00:22:42,300 --> 00:22:44,130
If you truly love me,

415
00:22:44,900 --> 00:22:47,270
you have to find out
where Seo Rin is and tell me.

416
00:22:48,640 --> 00:22:53,210
It's the only way for you to even begin
to atone for what Chae Hwa Young has done.

417
00:22:56,310 --> 00:22:57,310
Jun Ho,

418
00:22:58,480 --> 00:22:59,480
I'm begging you.

419
00:23:25,940 --> 00:23:27,210
(Daehan Genomics Center)

420
00:23:29,210 --> 00:23:31,410
(DNA Test Results)

421
00:23:33,820 --> 00:23:36,150
(Chae Hwa Young and Kang Jun Ho...)

422
00:23:36,150 --> 00:23:38,890
(indicate a 99.99 percent probability
of a maternal relationship.)

423
00:23:39,360 --> 00:23:40,820
Once Grandfather sees this,

424
00:23:41,460 --> 00:23:43,930
it's all over for you, Chae Hwa Young.

425
00:23:44,490 --> 00:23:46,530
You're going to pay for every crime
your greed has caused,

426
00:23:47,060 --> 00:23:48,370
and you'll pay for it all at once.

427
00:24:01,550 --> 00:24:04,150
Baek Ho, I need to see you.

428
00:24:10,220 --> 00:24:11,220
Jang Mi.

429
00:24:12,120 --> 00:24:13,190
What's wrong?

430
00:24:13,790 --> 00:24:15,130
Please, just hold me.

431
00:24:20,160 --> 00:24:21,160
What's wrong?

432
00:24:22,570 --> 00:24:23,800
Why are you shaking so much?

433
00:24:24,630 --> 00:24:27,370
Please, don't say anything.

434
00:24:31,040 --> 00:24:32,140
Baek Ho...

435
00:24:32,680 --> 00:24:36,010
I told Jun Ho everything. All of it.

436
00:24:36,980 --> 00:24:40,580
It was the only way
to stop my marriage to Jun Ho.

437
00:24:41,650 --> 00:24:43,850
I don't know what the fallout will be.

438
00:24:44,490 --> 00:24:48,860
But after learning what his mother did,
Jun Ho will never choose me.

439
00:24:49,760 --> 00:24:52,460
And, we can put an end to all of this.

440
00:24:53,560 --> 00:24:57,300
I just pray Grandfather doesn't collapse
from the shock.

441
00:25:00,900 --> 00:25:01,910
Tell me what's wrong.

442
00:25:02,670 --> 00:25:03,670
What's going on?

443
00:25:06,740 --> 00:25:09,110
I love you, Baek Ho.

444
00:25:10,880 --> 00:25:11,880
I love you too.

445
00:25:13,750 --> 00:25:14,820
I love you more...

446
00:25:16,120 --> 00:25:17,490
than my own life, Jang Mi.

447
00:25:34,240 --> 00:25:37,340
Here. I've been saving this for you.

448
00:25:37,410 --> 00:25:39,240
It's money I've been saving up,
little by little.

449
00:25:41,240 --> 00:25:42,510
Use it for your wedding.

450
00:25:45,680 --> 00:25:47,250
It may not seem like a lot,

451
00:25:47,750 --> 00:25:49,350
but this is just the beginning.

452
00:25:50,050 --> 00:25:53,460
From now on, I'll give you so much more.

453
00:25:54,120 --> 00:25:55,160
So, just stay with your mother...

454
00:25:55,690 --> 00:25:56,690
Enough!

455
00:25:58,190 --> 00:25:59,730
You shameless murderer!

456
00:26:00,360 --> 00:26:01,360
Jun Ho.

457
00:26:02,030 --> 00:26:03,230
What's gotten into you?

458
00:26:03,230 --> 00:26:05,270
Jun Ho!

459
00:26:06,270 --> 00:26:08,070
I never want to hear you
say my name again.

460
00:26:09,670 --> 00:26:10,910
You stole Ma Seo Rin's life,

461
00:26:11,510 --> 00:26:14,380
tried to kill Oh Jang Mi
and put Seo Rin in a coma instead,

462
00:26:14,780 --> 00:26:15,810
and still,

463
00:26:16,150 --> 00:26:19,020
knowing she was Oh Jang Mi,
you tried to make me marry her?

464
00:26:20,450 --> 00:26:22,650
- What?
- Is that how badly you wanted Dream?

465
00:26:23,650 --> 00:26:25,320
So you'd use me, your own son,

466
00:26:25,890 --> 00:26:27,790
to get me to marry Oh Jang Mi?

467
00:26:29,990 --> 00:26:31,760
So, are you going to kill Ma Seo Rin next?

468
00:26:32,430 --> 00:26:35,400
- Who in the world told you that?
- That's enough.

469
00:26:35,970 --> 00:26:37,070
CEO Chae Hwa Young.

470
00:26:38,470 --> 00:26:40,600
It's time to drop the shameless act...

471
00:26:41,910 --> 00:26:43,570
and stop all the lies.

472
00:26:44,980 --> 00:26:49,180
I am now disgusted
and sick to death of you as a person.

473
00:26:50,410 --> 00:26:51,780
Did Seo Rin tell you?

474
00:26:52,680 --> 00:26:55,890
No, did that witch, Oh Jang Mi,
run her mouth to you?

475
00:26:56,420 --> 00:26:57,690
It's all lies.

476
00:26:58,090 --> 00:27:01,520
She holds a grudge against me
over her father's death,

477
00:27:01,590 --> 00:27:03,560
so she's just spouting
whatever lies she can think of.

478
00:27:04,460 --> 00:27:05,460
In that case,

479
00:27:06,360 --> 00:27:08,400
who's the woman at the company right now?

480
00:27:09,800 --> 00:27:10,800
Is it Oh Jang Mi?

481
00:27:11,700 --> 00:27:12,770
Or Ma Seo Rin?

482
00:27:13,700 --> 00:27:15,410
Answer me that.

483
00:27:17,110 --> 00:27:18,110
Well...

484
00:27:57,950 --> 00:27:59,450
(The First Man)

485
00:27:59,520 --> 00:28:04,290
Director Ma went to see the Chairman,
carrying what looked like a DNA test.

486
00:28:04,520 --> 00:28:06,360
We have to shut Oh Jang Mi up
before she does.

487
00:28:07,290 --> 00:28:08,320
You punks.

488
00:28:09,660 --> 00:28:12,130
Chae Hwa Young. How dare you hurt Baek Ho?

489
00:28:12,960 --> 00:28:16,100
Isn't it odd
that Manager Lee isn't involved...

490
00:28:16,100 --> 00:28:17,400
in that car accident at all?

491
00:28:17,900 --> 00:28:20,240
What is your relationship
with Manager Lee?

492
00:28:20,570 --> 00:28:23,470
Chae Hwa Young,
you're not going to get your way.

493
00:28:27,240 --> 00:28:29,250
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
